This is a brand page for the GLOBAL STRATEGIC MANAGEMENT trademark by Global Strategic Management, Inc. 
                                in Annapolis, MD, 21401.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this GLOBAL STRATEGIC MANAGEMENT trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner Global Strategic Management, Inc. of the GLOBAL STRATEGIC MANAGEMENT trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the GLOBAL STRATEGIC MANAGEMENT trademark.
                           






On Wednesday, April 19, 1995,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        GLOBAL STRATEGIC MANAGEMENT by 
                        Global Strategic Management, Inc., Annapolis, MD  21401.
                        The USPTO has given the GLOBAL STRATEGIC MANAGEMENT 
                        trademark serial  number of  74678156.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is REGISTERED AND RENEWED.
                        The correspondent listed for GLOBAL STRATEGIC MANAGEMENT is 
                        
                        
                                            Joan Fagan Teich, Esq. of 
                                            THE TEICH LAW FIRM, LLC,  Suite 196, 554 N. Frederick Ave. Gaithersburg MD 20877
                                .
                            The GLOBAL STRATEGIC MANAGEMENT trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Insurance & Financial Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for GLOBAL STRATEGIC MANAGEMENT 
                            is investment management and consulting services in global stocks and bonds. 
                            





