GSMI MEMBERSHIP APPLICATION Membership Types: 1) Distinguished Fellow, 2)Fellow and 3) Regular Member  CURRENT LIST OF JOURNALS 1.            International Journal of Global Business, 2.            Journal of Economic Development, Management, IT, Finance and Marketing 3.            Journal of Marketing and Management; 4.            Journal of Information Technology and Economic Development, 5.            Journal of Finance, Accounting and Management,  The journals are indexed in EBSCO and Cabell’s Directories; Some quality papers/abstracts are  indexed with prestigious indexes such as NASA ADS (Harvard University Library),  INSPEC, DBLP, Google Scholar, DOI,  Scirus,  ProQuest and IJCA. The journals are also under consideration by SCOPUS and ISI Publishing  Distinguished Fellowship  and Fellowship are awarded only by nominations/invitations based on exhibition of leadership qualities  Membership is by application:  If you are interested in becoming a GSMI member, please complete and return the Membership Form along with your  CV/resume in MS Word DOCX   and send as email attachment to mhkuofie_gsmi@msn.com, gsmi_usa@msn.com  BENEFITS FOR ANNUAL DISTINGUISHED FELLOWSHIP 1.      Opportunity to negotiate agreement on behalf of GSMI  2.      Opportunity to represent GSMI at international activities3.      Free attendance to all GSMI activities all over the world4.      Special Distinguished Fellowship Plaque5.      Plus benefits for fellowship and regular membership below BENEFITS FOR ANNUAL FELLOWSHIP Lead GSMI activities academic courses in many countriesOpportunity to become a keynote speaker at international activityPlus benefits for regular membership below  BENEFITS FOR ANNUAL REGULAR MEMBERSHIP 1.      Become internationally known and can make a citation in bio-data/profile/resume.2.      Publish in GSMI international journal by paying a discounted processing fee3.       Opportunity to become an editor of GSMI journal(s), which is honorary  4.      Receive a membership certificate5.      Opportunity to serve as a consultant on international financial/capital investment, accounting, operations management, marketing and IT projects6.      You recommend (bring in) projects to GSMI7.      Be compensated for your participation in activities including teaching and consulting8.      Discount on GSMI fee charging activity  -such as conferences9.       Opportunity for internship with GSMI USA and/or GSMI global affiliates10.   Receive appropriate outstanding support for advancement to member’s career, including letters of support and doctoral dissertation support 11.  Opportunity to become a franchisee of GSMI and/or GSMI subsidiary(ies) franchise 12.   There is an annual performance review of each member  Renewal: Renewal of annual membership depends on the member earning satisfactory annual performance review of contribution of GSMI activities  ANNUAL/YEARLY MEMBERSHIP FEES Membership Type: Distinguished Fellow:                                  $795Fellow:                                                            $300Regular Member:Business  official:                           $200Professor/Research Scholar:        $150Student:                                          $100 For more information about GSMI, please go to:?? 






















